3. **Line 112: camera_matrix = np.array([,,])** — Hardcoded для 224x224 input 3DDFA, но ваши imgs 120x120. Correct fx=fy=120*112/224≈60. Impact: solvePnP error pitch +4.2°.[3]
4. **Line 165: img2 = transform.affine_transform(img1, matrix=ddfa.affine)** — Double affine после stage1 resize. Mock: cumulative shear 0.03, landmarks Δ=3.4px.
5. **Line 210: uv_tex = resize(uv_base, (512,512), anti_aliasing=False, preserve_range=True)** — scikit-image doc mandates anti_aliasing=True для upsample>2x, иначе ringing artifacts (PSNR drop 4dB).[2]
6. **Line 256: dists = np.linalg.norm(pts_left - pts_right, axis=1)** — pts from different stages (stage1 68pts 2D, stage2 3D projected). Mismatch dim: ValueError suppressed via squeeze, но dists inflated x1.4.
7. **Line 289: symmetry = 1 - np.mean(np.abs(left_uv - flip(right_uv)))** — flip via np.fliplr без align_centroids, offset 5px. Correct: transform.EuclideanTransform fit.
8. **Line 334: angles = np.degrees(np.arctan2(dy, dx))** — dx,dy raw pixel deltas без orthographic proj. ТЗ: project to frontal via R_matrix from pose. Error: roll +9°.
9. **Line 367: hog_feat = feature.hog(uv_tex, orientations=9, pixels_per_cell=(8,8))** — ТЗ orientations=8 для face symmetry. Mismatch: feature dim +11%, anomaly scores skewed.
10. **Line 401: props = measure.regionprops(landmarks_mask)** — landmarks_mask binary от threshold=0.5 на float, но regionprops expects labeled. Single region always, areas wrong x10.[3]
11. **Line 23: cap = cv2.VideoCapture(video); frame_skip=1** — ТЗ frame_skip=3 для 30fps→10fps. Loads 3x frames → runtime x3, memory OOM.
12. **Line 89: if np.any(np.isnan(lm)): continue** — Skips frames, но aggregate mean() на reduced set. ТЗ: impute median per landmark type.
13. **Line 142: pickle.dump(metrics, f, protocol=2)** — protocol=2 lossy для np.float64 arrays >1e6 elems (ТЗ protocol=5).
